snippet.title: TransOcean Trailer
snippet.description: TransOcean – The Shipping Company is your ticket to the world of gigantic ships and running a transnational shipping empire.  Build a mighty fleet of modern merchant ships and conquer the seven seas as you track your routes in real time, take the controls as ships enter and leave harbours worldwide and see to it that freight gets loaded and unloaded efficiently. Choose from 55 of the largest and most exotic ports in the world to sail to and from.  A highly polished bonus system will lend an element of suspense to every decision.
